Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.59,0:01:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.34,0:02:01.58,OP-jp-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}曇り空覗いた予感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.47,0:01:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I...
