Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.67,0:09:47.66,JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ならば 普段どおりにしていてもいいようなものだが
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but with no key available we didn't have much choice.
