Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.96,0:26:51.76,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,150)\blur2}Let us meet in a blissful dream tonight, let it be our love
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.56,0:26:55.60,ED-jp-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}きっと　ねぇ見つけてね
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.76,0:26:55.76,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,150)\blur2}Find me, I beg you
